{"tid":861342,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個被人呃嘅經歷","createTime":"2018-10-14T05:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T10:28:20.000Z","uid":67434,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9ddb98b29783f4583207581a0f2e6ff8571390","tid":861342,"uid":67434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:12:19.000Z","msg":"細個嗰陣樓下有間租碟鋪執笠清貨<br />\n咁屋企有部DVD 機咪去睇下有冇筍嘢執<br />\n咁我就揀咗隻 超人迪加電影（$20) 同一隻 蒙面超人 555 劇場版（$30)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到收銀處係個 2x 歲嘅哥哥<br />\n佢見到就同我講：夾埋 50蚊 , 收你平啲 , 30蚊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我聽到梗係好開心喇，慳返$20喎。<br />\n<br />\n我以為佢見我細佬仔，就收平啲。<br />\n點知返到屋企拆盒，見到隻 555 得個吉盒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我落返去同佢講，叫佢退錢<br />\n佢指住張紙<br />\n上面寫住：貨一出門 恕不退換  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30472bcae09d3c80f7ca85dcba90c48009418854","tid":861342,"uid":128600,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"幫你儲起利是錢<br />\n大過比返你"},{"pid":"b317656eac72eeefd560363c086b32ecec14ebae","tid":861342,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"巨商100LV騎射換左隻1LV騎狼"},{"pid":"95a23db394c2b896ace7aa17939f06fff5dc8910","tid":861342,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:14:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb449c8dd970bb3cdcdb2d19453f316305c74a09","tid":861342,"uid":1367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:14:24.000Z","msg":"Online game買武器"},{"pid":"c911bf38056